    <description>&lt;DIV&gt;There is some good discussion here.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;As someone mentioned, we saw a lot of feedback requesting that&amp;nbsp;faction-related content make a return to EverQuest.&amp;nbsp; Dark Reign and Norrath's Keepers are what we felt was a fair summary of what the community was asking for on a smaller scale.&amp;nbsp; We wanted to make it flexible and balanced and not restrictive.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;So, we've been watching feedback and generally&amp;nbsp;reviewing how well this faction direction is&amp;nbsp;liked and then we'll see if it's a style of play that works for the community.&amp;nbsp; So, the more feedback we get around the "fun" and "interest" with factioning on this smaller scale, the better we can see where to take it.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Thanks!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
